Now this way you can say:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">if&#40;$words&#91;0&#93; == &quot;ymera&quot; &amp;&amp; $words&#91;1&#93; != &quot;botname&quot; &amp;&amp; $faction == &quot;Neutral&quot;&#41;</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
